StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
(@ProgramCode varchar(4) ,@ProgramType varchar(4) ,@PregramDesc varchar(60) ,@Incep.onDate date.me ,@Status varchar(1) ,@UserLogin varchar(15))
AS
INSERT INTO [dbo].[PROGRAM] ([PROGRAM_CODE] ,[PROGRAM_TYPE] ,[PROGRAM_DESCRIPTION] ,[INCEPTION_DATE] ,[STATUS] ,[USER_LOGIN] ,[UPDATE_DATE]) VALUES (@ProgramCode ,@ProgramType ,@PregramDesc ,@Incep.onDate ,@Status ,@UserLogin ,GetDate())
